snippet.title: FilmIsNow Action Movie Trailers
snippet.description:
Welcome to Filmisnow ACTION MOVIE TRAILERS channel your one stop channel for all that is action including high energy, big-budget physical stunts and chases, battles, fights, escapes, destructive crises (floods, explosions, natural disasters, fires, etc.), 'good-guy/girl' vs 'bad guy/girl' all designed for pure audience escapism. Included are the James Bond 'fantasy' spy/espionage series, martial arts films, so-called 'blaxploitation' films, and the big block-buster superhero movies.

The FILMISNOW Network is one of YouTube's TOP 15 film & animation channels worldwide. Thanks to our viewers who love movies, our network generates more than 60 million monthly views through our seven channels
